Description: FluentMail |Build Status| |PyPI|
        --------------------------------
        
        Python SMTP client and Email for Humansâ„¢
        
        Simple
        ------
        
        FluentMail tries to keep it simple as possible.
        
        Install
        -------
        
        ``pip install fluentmail``
        
        Compatibility
        -------------
        
        Works with Python 2.6+, Python 3.3+, PyPy and PyPy 3.
        
        Documentation
        -------------
        
        You can find some info on the project wiki.
        
        Features
        --------
        
        -  SMTP
        -  Mailgun
        -  Plain or HTML body
        -  Alternative body
        -  Attachments
        
        Future work
        -----------
        
        -  More test coverage
        -  Dummy backend
        -  FileBased backend
        -  MemoryBased backend
        -  Support template engines (Django, Jinja)
        -  Support custom message headers
        -  Set default backend
        -  Thread-safety
        -  Inline attachment
        -  What more?
        
